      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOONLIGHT RIVER (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (35.27) at this track behind Mepunga Infrared in a Grade 5/6. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Key chance in this line up. IVORY PYGMY (4) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only one length from Appellant in third (23.56) at this track. Can measure up. ADHANA LAYLA (2) scored a most impressive win two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 21 length 4th at Angle Park (36.03). Can figure in the finish. OLLIE LIMES (3) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to atone.",
